   <title>Web Page</title>
   <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css">
   <script type = "module" src="script.js"></script>


</head>

<input type="text" id="todo" placeholder="Enter a todo" onkeypress="addTodo(event)">
placeholder: a hint to the user of what can be entered into the field
onkeypress: event that occurs when a key is pressed
addTodo: function to add a todo
event: the event object

//window.onload = function() { //code here } : run the code when the page is loaded



#document

//return the document object
document.querySelector('h1'): returns the first h1 element in the document
document.getElemntbyid('id'): returns the element with the specified id
// return a list 
document.querySelectorAll('selector'): returns a list of elements that match the specified selector
document.getElementsByClassName('class'): returns a list of elements that match the specified class
document.getElementsByTagName('tag'): returns a list of elements that match the specified tag
document.getElementsByName('name'): returns a list of elements that match the specified name

onfocus() : event that occurs when an element gets focus ( được chọn)
onblur() : event that occurs when an element loses focus ( mất focus)

